name: A+E:KKK - BORNTOBURN001
description: A+E:KKK - BORNTOBURN001 (BUY TO BURN) - AMO+ESCLAVO - (MASTER+SLAVE) is the name given to a group of works that have been done in different formats and media. In AMO+ESCLAVO I try to express my concerns in painting, drawing or in a combination of both with the tools offered by new technologies.
